## 🎯 Project Overview

This repository contains the work completed as part of the **CFSS Global Internship Program 2026** under the project:

### 🔍 The Vulnerability Report Card - End-to-End VAPT Simulation

The project focuses on:

✅ Reconnaissance  
✅ Enumeration  
✅ Vulnerability Research  
✅ Vulnerability Validation  
✅ Risk Assessment  
✅ Professional Reporting

